            ['A security wave', 'HEAD output rebuilt through a sanitising allowlist, CSRF exemptions matched on path boundaries, oversized form posts failing loud.', 'v0.4.3'],
            ['Multi-core serving', 'pyxle serve --workers N: independent server processes per core, sync endpoints threadpooled, small assets served from memory. This site runs it.', 'v0.4.3'],
